  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 200°C.",
    "In a large pan, heat the oil over medium heat.",
    "Add the grated carrots and onions and cook until they start to soften.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the drained sauerkraut and cook until it starts to brown.",
    "Add the halal-friendly pork sausages and cook until browned on all sides.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a terracotta dish and sprinkle the breadcrumbs over the top.",
    "Drizzle the beef broth over the breadcrumbs and dust with flour.",
    "Transfer the dish to the preheated oven and cook for 20 minutes.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with chopped fresh parsley if desired."
